---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Blog | Karen Arze">
  <h1 style="color: #003366; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">Personal Reflections</h1>

  <article style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #eef2f7; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
    <div style="width: 100%; height: 300px; background: #f0f7ff; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; border-bottom: 1px solid #eef2f7;">
      <p style="color: #a2c2e1; font-style: italic;">[Place a picture of your new home or graduation here]</p>
    </div>

    <div style="padding: 30px;">
      <h2 style="color: #0056b3; margin-top: 0;">A Season of Gratitude</h2>
      <p style="line-height: 1.8; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #333;">
        I am so grateful for the blessings I have been given in this lifetime. Both my children are about to graduate, I'm finally a homeowner <strong>[Yay!]</strong>, and ***** Eye Care has provided me the perfect environment and tools needed to become an even better version of myself.
      </p>

      <div style="margin-top: 30px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0; padding-top: 20px;">
        <button style="background: #f0f7ff; border: none; color: #0056b3; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 30px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold;">❤️ Heart This Post</button>
        <div style="color: #999; font-size: 0.9rem;">12 Likes</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
